item.title: CVE-2022-36900|2024-08-03T10:14:29.482Z -- jenkins%20project -- jenkins%20compuware%20zadviser%20api%20plugin
item.description: Jenkins Compuware zAdviser API Plugin 1.0.3 and earlier does not restrict execution of a controller/agent message to agents, allowing attackers able to control agent processes to retrieve Java system properties.
